---
import Container from '../shared/Container.astro';
---

<section class="py-12 md:py-16">
  <Container>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card px-8 py-12 text-center shadow-sm md:px-12 md:py-14">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-3xl">
        准备好提升社区活跃度了吗？
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-md text-muted-foreground">
        从绑定账号到自动发布，SendFox 让高校社区运营变成一件轻松的事
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <a
          href="/docs/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-primary/90"
        >
          阅读快速上手指南
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
